Method:

1. Method is a function
2. method name should be followed by paranthesis()
3. method name should be in camel case
4. Method get executed when it is called.
5. We need to call the method by it's name.


Example:

public class HelloWorld
{
    public static void main(String[]args)
    {
          first();
        
    }
    
    public static void first()
    {
      System.out.println("first");
        
        System.out.println("first1");
    }
    
}
